Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In the previous episode, we talked about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie and Sparky want to ask Slowy to become the basketball team’s coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,During this time, Champ and Shu Er came to take over the Goats’ Village basketball court.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, a masked expert appeared and defeated Champ and Shu Er.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It turns out he was Slowy’s old classmate, Blazey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The map the village chief gave us showed that it was in this vicinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a house there
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally found
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:01:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! I’m about to meet the mighty Blazey senior!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This imposing figure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He was still holding a basketball in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Before Blazey
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,generation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.60,0:01:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, grandpa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Weslie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.56,0:01:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who I am is unimportant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The important thing is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re blocking my way home
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we’ll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:01:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You said this is your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you’re Blazey senior?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Blazey senior? You’ve mistaken me for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie, it seems we’ve come to the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he really not Blazey’s senior?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s you guys again! You all said you’d got the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The goat needs to use the toilet urgently. May I borrow it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can’t
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to finish this quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, this old man’s house was quite tidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The toilet is over there, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay… okay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This outfit looks so familiar…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,let me see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This straw hat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this yours, grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, going to the restroom was just an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I wanted to come in and confirm something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Blazey injured his leg after helping him that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And like you, he also has an injury to his right leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus this straw hat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s exactly the same as the one Blazey wore back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It really looks like it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re Blazey’s senior, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be our coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a straw hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s just a raincoat, an essential item for home use.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As for this…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m getting old and my legs and feet are having some problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Applying medicine is normal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If there’s nothing else, hurry up and go, I need to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Basketball game
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, you still play basketball games?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t this a football game? It’s really popular lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:05:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This soccer game is so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t that a basketball?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You don’t mean to tell me that it’s football, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t that a soccer ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you kidding? Any normal person would know that’s a basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone there? Could you help me retrieve the soccer ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There really are people who get it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going out to return the ball, you guys should hurry up and go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful when you kick next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,let’s go
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he’s really not a Blazey veteran anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I still think he’s Blazey’s senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,old man
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m tidying up the room and cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You clearly wanted to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be Blazey, please be our coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior, you promised us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re the ones blocking me from sweeping the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let our seniors feel our sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior, why don’t you take a nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I’ll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to us with confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior, wait a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,senior
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s really troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t be afraid, senior, we’ll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,senior
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, senior?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, could he have fainted from his injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to hurry up and find a doctor for our senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you fall asleep like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of a master
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find a way to get up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me, I can climb up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for my good news
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit more
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have some misunderstanding about the concept of “a little bit” white?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any other methods?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s a tree branch on that cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we tie vines to the stones
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:09:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then put the stone through the hole and tie it to the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We were able to climb up easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But that circle doesn’t seem easy to throw in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch me this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My footwork is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain… Oh, it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s still too difficult to hit the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we try a different shooting form?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A proper shooting form will definitely increase your shooting percentage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But my shooting form doesn’t seem to be quite standard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shooting is also inaccurate
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll teach you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it reliable or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s definitely reliable; I’ve studied many basketball stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They are all like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I put my hands like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it should be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, jump up and throw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what shooting feels like!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt my hands starting to boil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t be so tense, relax a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So tired
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s too far away
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The stone fork was so heavy that my hand shape changed when I threw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, as long as we don’t give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It will definitely succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior, you’re awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,senior
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thankfully, Blazey was there just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, the senior asked us for advice on playing basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.76,0:12:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We will definitely study hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I will absolutely not give up halfway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be our coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,senior
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,senior…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
